[Donut.Launcher.exe] ..> [Start-Donut.ps1] : hosts / launches
[Start-Donut.ps1] ..> [DonutApp.ps1] : dot-sources
[DonutApp.ps1] ..> [MainPresenter] : initializes
[MainPresenter] ..> [MainWindow.xaml] : manages
[MainPresenter] ..> [HomePresenter] : creates

[HomePresenter] ..> [HomeView.xaml] : binds
[HomePresenter] ..> [ScanService] : scan
[HomePresenter] ..> [RemoteUpdateService] : updates
[HomePresenter] ..> [InventoryService] : per-machine probe
[HomePresenter] ..> [DiskUsageService] : storage scan
[HomePresenter] ..> [HostResolver] : prefetch IP
[HomePresenter] ..> [ActiveDirectoryService] : live AD finder
[HomePresenter] ..> [AsyncJob] : queues
[HomePresenter] ..> [RecentConnectionsStore] : persists
[HomePresenter] ..> [ScanCacheDecision] : 24h reuse

[ScanService] ..> [ExecutionService]
[RemoteUpdateService] ..> [ExecutionService]
[InventoryService] ..> [ExecutionService]
[DiskUsageService] ..> [ExecutionService]
[RemoteUpdateService] ..> [DriverMatchingService]

[ExecutionService] ..> [RemoteWorker.ps1] : invokes via PsExec
[ActiveDirectoryService] ..> [AdSearchWorker.ps1] : LDAP query
[ActiveDirectoryService] ..> [AdUnlockWorker.ps1] : unlock account
[AsyncJob] ..> [RunspaceManager] : uses pool

[ConfigPresenter] ..> [ConfigManager]
[ConfigManager] ..> [AppConfig]
[ConfigManager] ..> [config/]

[UpdatePresenter] ..> [SelfUpdateService]
[LoginPresenter] ..> [SelfUpdateService]
[SelfUpdateService] ..> [InstallWorker.ps1] : invokes
@enduml
